{"id":21678,"date":"2022-06-27T10:32:36","date_gmt":"2022-06-27T08:32:36","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/www.mannheimerswartling.se\/?p=21678"},"modified":"2022-06-27T15:43:17","modified_gmt":"2022-06-27T13:43:17","slug":"belfor-forvarvar-nordic-group-fran-polaris","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/www.mannheimerswartling.se\/uppdrag\/belfor-forvarvar-nordic-group-fran-polaris\/","title":{"rendered":"Belfor f\u00f6rv\u00e4rvar Nordic Group fr\u00e5n Polaris"},"content":{"rendered":"<p class=\"preamble\">Belfor har f\u00f6rv\u00e4rvat Nordic SSG Group A\/S, en ledande nordisk skadeservicekoncern, fr\u00e5n Polaris Private Equity.<\/p>\n<p>Skadeservicekoncernen SSG Group grundades i Danmark och inkluderar bland annat de svenska dotterbolagen EBE Gruppen och Ovento. SSG Group har under Polaris \u00e4gande gjort ett antal f\u00f6rv\u00e4rv som gjort dem till ett av de ledande leverant\u00f6rerna av skadetj\u00e4nster i Norden.<\/p>\n<p>Belfor har 11 100 anst\u00e4llda v\u00e4rlden \u00f6ver och har mer \u00e4n 40 \u00e5rs erfarenhet av hela v\u00e4rdekedjan fr\u00e5n skadestopp till \u00e5teruppbyggnad.<\/p>\n<p>Mannheimer Swartling r\u00e5dgav Belfor i f\u00f6rh\u00e5llande till svensk r\u00e4tt i transaktionen.<\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>Belfor har f\u00f6rv\u00e4rvat Nordic SSG Group A\/S, en ledande nordisk skadeservicekoncern, fr\u00e5n Polaris Private Equity. Skadeservicekoncernen SSG Group grundades i Danmark och inkluderar bland annat\u2026<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":16,"featured_media":21685,"comment_status":"open","ping_status":"open","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"_acf_changed":false,"footnotes":""},"categories":[3469],"tags":[],"class_list":["post-21678","post","type-post","status-publish","format-standard","has-post-thumbnail","hentry","category-uppdrag","business-group-corporate-commercial","business-group-fastighetsratt","business-group-foretagsoverlatelser"],"acf":[],"lang":"sv